1
00:01:36,980 --> 00:01:38,000
=Snow Fall=

2
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,650
=Snow Fall=
=Episode 23=

3
00:01:40,650 --> 00:01:41,940
(This is a work of fiction.)

4
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:48,780
(Haidong Army HQ)

5
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,030
You may go inside.

6
00:01:51,210 --> 00:01:52,880
Superintendent Wu
agrees with seeing you.

7
00:01:53,430 --> 00:01:54,200
Thank you.

8
00:02:00,260 --> 00:02:00,790
Have a seat.

9
00:02:01,410 --> 00:02:02,560
Thank you, Superintendent Wu.

10
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:11,080
Superintendent Wu, I didn't expect you
to be generous enough to see me in person.

11
00:02:11,110 --> 00:02:12,360
Let me thank you in advance.

12
00:02:12,510 --> 00:02:13,990
Miss Jin, you're capable.

13
00:02:14,230 --> 00:02:15,760
Why would you become dejected

14
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,950
over such a small affair?

15
00:02:17,450 --> 00:02:18,920
Even if you have to make a comeback,

16
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:22,080
I'm sure it's nothing difficult for you.

17
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:25,440
Superintendent Wu, you do know
how to assess the situation.

18
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:28,040
If not, you wouldn't have
gotten to where you are today.

19
00:02:29,270 --> 00:02:30,810
Miss Jin, thank you for the compliment.

20
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:33,040
So, what brings you here today?

21
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:40,080
I heard that the Haidong Army
cleaned up the mine.

22
00:02:41,270 --> 00:02:42,600
I just found out

23
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,990
that Li Yingliang died inside the mine.

24
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:49,090
Fallen leaves return to their roots
like how we return to our ancestry.

25
00:02:49,670 --> 00:02:51,760
He was from the Jin family after all.

26
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:55,200
I have to find his body and
give him a proper burial.

27
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:56,670
Superintendent Wu,

28
00:02:57,230 --> 00:02:58,480
will you help me out?

29
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,040
Miss Jin,

30
00:03:02,550 --> 00:03:03,440
to be honest,

31
00:03:03,990 --> 00:03:06,600
not only did the mine collapse,
but there was also a huge fire.

32
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,760
Our men did inspect the place.

33
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,760
We didn't see Li Yingliang's body.

34
00:05:01,270 --> 00:05:02,640
His body wasn't found?

35
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:07,120
That means Liang is still alive,

36
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:10,080
right?

37
00:05:14,590 --> 00:05:15,390
Right?

38
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:05,390
Mother, here.

39
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:09,830
Thank you, Qian.

40
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,200
Here.

41
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,470
Put it on for me.

42
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,590
Your father did the same for me

43
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,950
back then.

44
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:45,560
My solitary shadow lingers in the world.

45
00:06:47,150 --> 00:06:48,910
How can we share life

46
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:52,120
but not death?

47
00:07:21,590 --> 00:07:22,350
(Love.)

48
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:24,680
(What exactly is love?)

49
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,910
(Must we love something
once we obtain it?)

50
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,760
(Must we cry)

51
00:07:30,910 --> 00:07:32,350
(when we lose it?)

52
00:08:06,830 --> 00:08:07,710
Big Brother,

53
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,830
when I courted Jingxue in the past,

54
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,190
it was as if I was worshiping a Buddha.

55
00:08:15,510 --> 00:08:17,000
I would be elated

56
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,240
as long as she was wearing

57
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,880
something I bought.

58
00:08:20,910 --> 00:08:23,120
Now, although she's living with me,

59
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,710
I don't feel happy at all.

60
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,320
In the past,

61
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,440
I knew that she loved Li Yingliang.

62
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:30,910
But I thought

63
00:08:31,470 --> 00:08:32,590
it didn't matter.

64
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:35,390
You can like whoever you like
and I can do the same.

65
00:08:35,590 --> 00:08:36,950
Liking someone is my own business.

66
00:08:37,310 --> 00:08:38,520
It's fine as long as I'm happy.

67
00:08:39,590 --> 00:08:40,440
But today,

68
00:08:40,920 --> 00:08:42,350
I only found out

69
00:08:42,950 --> 00:08:44,320
that I didn't care about her.

70
00:08:44,410 --> 00:08:45,710
I just cared about obtaining her.

71
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,280
But in her heart,

72
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,680
there are no traces of me at all.

73
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,110
Big Brother,

74
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,350
you didn't see how she was crying today.

75
00:08:53,990 --> 00:08:55,160
I felt a little terrified.

76
00:08:55,980 --> 00:08:57,520
I was afraid that she would keep crying,

77
00:08:57,830 --> 00:08:59,040
just like my mother.

78
00:09:00,950 --> 00:09:03,110
I only encountered
one person I liked after so long.

79
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,040
If she cries herself to death,

80
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,110
wouldn't that be quite a shame for me?

81
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,320
That would be a shame.

82
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:18,870
I have to make her happy.

83
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,350
Wu, stop at the junction.

84
00:09:40,350 --> 00:09:41,180
Buy some newspapers.

85
00:09:42,830 --> 00:09:44,400
Wu, I'm talking to you. Did you hear me?

86
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:46,750
Wu...

87
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:53,320
There's a street called
Xinglong Street in Haidong.

88
00:10:55,230 --> 00:10:57,200
There are plenty of interesting things

89
00:10:57,630 --> 00:10:58,680
and delicious food there.

90
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:01,630
When I first came to Haidong,

91
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:03,590
I went there with Weilian once.

92
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:06,350
It's very lively.

93
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,200
You should check it out.

94
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:20,710
You can make a candy figure.

95
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:23,110
They sell roasted chestnuts

96
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:25,440
and candied hawthorns as well.

97
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:30,080
You can watch
acrobatic performances there.

98
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,760
There are plenty
of other things there.

99
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:42,780
♪Hands that have explored the world♪

100
00:11:44,300 --> 00:11:51,180
♪Other than colors, I have everything♪

101
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:56,440
(Mi Lan.)

102
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:58,870
(It's a shame)

103
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,710
(that I can't keep you company.)

104
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,350
(But I still hope)

105
00:12:03,350 --> 00:12:05,990
(that you can enjoy
the wonders of the world more often.)

106
00:12:43,940 --> 00:12:46,820
♪You'll always be the moon
in the night sky♪

107
00:12:47,220 --> 00:12:51,900
♪No matter if you're the full moon
or the new moon♪

108
00:12:52,540 --> 00:12:54,140
♪Let me enjoy it to the fullest♪

109
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:57,420
♪Soberly, without any restraints♪

110
00:12:57,420 --> 00:13:01,020
♪As I run toward love♪

111
00:13:01,260 --> 00:13:04,220
♪I don't care♪

112
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:09,300
♪That my sights
were deeply affected by darkness♪

113
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:11,460
♪When your firm♪

114
00:13:11,460 --> 00:13:14,340
♪And warm arms embrace me♪

115
00:13:14,340 --> 00:13:21,620
♪Become my salvation♪

116
00:13:47,950 --> 00:13:50,750
Mr. Shen!

117
00:13:52,590 --> 00:13:53,830
Mr. Shen!

118
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:56,590
Mr. Shen, I'm back.

119
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,590
I bought candied hawthorns
and roasted chestnuts.

120
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:02,710
Welcome back.

121
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:08,920
I'll peel them for you.

122
00:14:31,870 --> 00:14:33,830
(Before this, she was blind.)

123
00:14:34,110 --> 00:14:36,350
(Now, not only can she see,)

124
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:38,630
(but she's extremely swift as well.)

125
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:43,590
(I'm sure this is related
to the Blood Amber Stone.)

126
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:04,950
Mr. Shen gave me plenty of nice things.

127
00:15:05,470 --> 00:15:07,230
I'm going to give him
something in return.

128
00:15:08,710 --> 00:15:10,590
That's why you guys have to be good

129
00:15:10,710 --> 00:15:11,870
and bloom,

130
00:15:12,350 --> 00:15:13,160
understood?

131
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:34,350
Madam, we've arrived.

132
00:15:35,350 --> 00:15:35,870
Please.

133
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:36,950
Okay.

134
00:15:40,750 --> 00:15:42,060
- Here you go.
- Thank you.

135
00:15:42,070 --> 00:15:49,500
(Mi Mansion)

136
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:19,880
(Haidong Maritime General Council)

137
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:22,260
(Haidong Maritime Industry Association)

138
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:24,710
Why did you bring me here?

139
00:16:25,550 --> 00:16:26,680
Are you trying to trigger me?

140
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:29,440
I owe you a birthday gift, right?

141
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,080
You'll find out when you go inside.

142
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:53,380
- Welcome, Miss Jin.
- Welcome, Miss Jin.

143
00:16:58,300 --> 00:17:00,060
(Miss Jin, welcome back
to being in charge again)

144
00:17:03,520 --> 00:17:05,910
Miss Jin, you should come back
and take over the association.

145
00:17:06,630 --> 00:17:07,110
Come back.

146
00:17:07,110 --> 00:17:08,080
That's right, Miss Jin.

147
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:09,790
- You should come back.
- You should come back.

148
00:17:10,350 --> 00:17:12,590
Second Uncle, what do you mean by this?

149
00:17:13,910 --> 00:17:14,830
Jingxue,

150
00:17:15,110 --> 00:17:17,630
I was just joking with you
a few days ago.

151
00:17:18,050 --> 00:17:19,760
How could I steal
the association from you?

152
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:21,040
I would be inhumane if I did so.

153
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:22,390
Take a look.

154
00:17:22,430 --> 00:17:24,150
This is the transfer agreement.

155
00:17:24,410 --> 00:17:25,670
I've already signed it for you.

156
00:17:25,760 --> 00:17:26,350
Look.

157
00:17:26,870 --> 00:17:30,320
The Jin family's real estate,
properties, and their keys,

158
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:32,480
all of them are here. Take them.

159
00:17:34,670 --> 00:17:35,520
You don't believe me?

160
00:17:35,670 --> 00:17:36,520
Why would I

161
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:38,800
call all of them here to receive you, then?

162
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:40,870
That's right, Miss Jin.

163
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:43,000
- Come back.
- Come back.

164
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:43,800
We're waiting for you.

165
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:45,080
We reserved your office for you.

166
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:46,910
Yeah. We already cleaned it up for you.

167
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:47,910
Let's go.

168
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:49,190
Miss Jin.

169
00:17:49,190 --> 00:17:49,680
Come back.

170
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,110
Miss Jin, you should come back.

171
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:51,720
That's right.

172
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:52,430
Please.

173
00:17:53,800 --> 00:17:55,190
Miss Jin, let's go.

174
00:17:55,630 --> 00:17:56,140
Let's go.

175
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:04,960
Are you satisfied?

176
00:18:06,830 --> 00:18:07,670
Not bad.

177
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:13,320
But if I find out
that you try to hurt Jingxue again,

178
00:18:14,330 --> 00:18:15,720
I'll come and "play" with you again.

179
00:18:31,660 --> 00:18:34,260
(Jinghua Restaurant)

180
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:46,320
Ancestors of the Shen family,

181
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:49,390
I've brought Zhiqian back.

182
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:53,190
Ancestors of the Shen family,

183
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:57,760
I, Shen Zhiqian, am here
to acknowledge my roots.

184
00:19:32,430 --> 00:19:32,960
Is it done?

185
00:19:35,240 --> 00:19:36,590
Here. Paste it on the wall.

186
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:37,080
Okay.

187
00:20:09,910 --> 00:20:11,390
Paste it over there. Go now.

188
00:20:24,480 --> 00:20:25,350
I'm done.

189
00:20:25,350 --> 00:20:25,800
Okay.

190
00:20:25,800 --> 00:20:26,560
I'm done too.

191
00:20:26,630 --> 00:20:28,280
Let's prepare
and make some dumplings.

192
00:20:33,910 --> 00:20:34,910
Who could it be?

193
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:40,240
Heng, I invited Jingxue to celebrate
the Chinese New Year with us.

194
00:20:41,390 --> 00:20:42,390
Alright. Go now.

195
00:20:45,110 --> 00:20:45,910
That's pretty good.

196
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:46,980
It'll be livelier.

197
00:20:49,110 --> 00:20:50,560
Big Brother, Jingxue is here.

198
00:20:51,910 --> 00:20:52,590
Mi Lan.

199
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:53,320
Jingxue.

200
00:20:54,280 --> 00:20:54,910
You're here.

201
00:20:57,040 --> 00:20:58,720
He insisted on dragging me here.

202
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:02,320
I guess I have no choice but to celebrate
the Chinese New Year with you guys.

203
00:21:02,700 --> 00:21:03,670
Happy Chinese New Year.

204
00:21:04,250 --> 00:21:05,190
Happy Chinese New Year.

205
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:08,090
It's good that you're visiting us.
No need to bring any gifts.

206
00:21:08,190 --> 00:21:09,080
Here, Mi Lan.

207
00:21:11,520 --> 00:21:13,350
That handbag is mine.

208
00:21:16,220 --> 00:21:18,190
Great timing.
Let's make some dumplings together.

209
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:18,960
Weilian.

210
00:21:19,830 --> 00:21:20,430
Come on.

211
00:21:21,440 --> 00:21:22,150
Jingxue, let's go.

212
00:21:36,560 --> 00:21:38,390
You guys are turning it
into a sticky mess.

213
00:21:38,430 --> 00:21:39,040
Stop it.

214
00:21:39,760 --> 00:21:40,520
Especially you.

215
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:41,800
Got it.

216
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:43,720
Jingxue,

217
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:45,350
how are you so good at this?

218
00:21:45,600 --> 00:21:47,830
Chinese New Year was
a lively occasion in the past.

219
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:50,150
Both my parents
and Liang were still around...

220
00:21:55,150 --> 00:21:56,670
Anyway, everyone was there.

221
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:58,720
Naturally, Chinese New Year
was a lot of fun.

222
00:21:59,530 --> 00:22:02,040
Don't tell me you guys never celebrated
Chinese New Year before?

223
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:04,350
I thought everyone knew
how to make dumplings.

224
00:22:04,870 --> 00:22:06,240
I lived alone for a long time.

225
00:22:06,250 --> 00:22:07,680
I never celebrated
Chinese New Year.

226
00:22:07,700 --> 00:22:09,190
Heng never taught me
how to celebrate.

227
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:11,240
I was blind since I was born.

228
00:22:11,280 --> 00:22:12,830
My parents argued often as well.

229
00:22:12,840 --> 00:22:15,580
We could only celebrate Chinese New Year
when they were in a good mood.

230
00:22:15,590 --> 00:22:16,990
Only then would I have dumplings.

231
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:18,150
But I couldn't see.

232
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:19,380
So I couldn't learn
how to make.

233
00:22:19,390 --> 00:22:21,830
If so, I guess I can teach you.

234
00:22:22,280 --> 00:22:23,280
Do you wish to learn?

235
00:22:24,150 --> 00:22:24,720
I do!

236
00:22:25,870 --> 00:22:26,800
Me too.

237
00:22:28,080 --> 00:22:29,190
I'll teach you two, then.

238
00:22:29,760 --> 00:22:30,520
Two folds.

239
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:31,080
Here.

240
00:22:34,910 --> 00:22:36,870
After that, pinch it gently

241
00:22:37,320 --> 00:22:37,870
in the middle.

242
00:22:37,870 --> 00:22:38,800
After that,

243
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:41,040
pinch both sides gently.

244
00:22:41,340 --> 00:22:42,560
Your dumpling is ready.

245
00:22:44,560 --> 00:22:46,190
Mr. Shen, does it look nice?

246
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:47,390
Yeah.

247
00:22:49,910 --> 00:22:50,590
Weilian.

248
00:22:52,720 --> 00:22:54,190
I intend to write another couplet.

249
00:22:54,350 --> 00:22:55,350
You should come with me.

250
00:22:55,910 --> 00:22:56,390
Alright.

251
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:57,990
You guys can continue.

252
00:23:02,630 --> 00:23:04,320
Did Shen Zhiheng turn you into this?

253
00:23:05,430 --> 00:23:06,560
You can tell Weilian

254
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:07,800
to convert you as well.

255
00:23:08,110 --> 00:23:08,960
I don't want that.

256
00:23:10,390 --> 00:23:11,670
You regained vision.

257
00:23:11,800 --> 00:23:13,390
Shen Zhiheng has immortality.

258
00:23:13,910 --> 00:23:15,870
Although I don't know
what Weilian has obtained,

259
00:23:16,040 --> 00:23:16,760
I think

260
00:23:16,760 --> 00:23:18,110
he did obtain a lot of benefits.

261
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:20,760
However, you guys are no longer humans.

262
00:23:21,350 --> 00:23:23,110
I think it's worth it.

263
00:23:24,350 --> 00:23:25,110
This way,

264
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:27,390
I can be together with Mr. Shen forever.

265
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:29,000
That's you.

266
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:29,930
Anyway, I don't want it.

267
00:23:30,150 --> 00:23:31,870
Why are you always angry?

268
00:23:31,960 --> 00:23:33,520
Why do you always look angry, then?

269
00:23:34,110 --> 00:23:35,590
I just look angry.

270
00:23:37,720 --> 00:23:39,630
I'll be nice to you in the future.

271
00:23:39,800 --> 00:23:41,590
I'll also be nice to Weilian
in the future.

272
00:23:42,280 --> 00:23:43,760
I'll make money for him to spend.

273
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,560
Shen Zhiheng is wealthy.

274
00:23:45,570 --> 00:23:46,860
He doesn't need you
to make money.

275
00:23:46,870 --> 00:23:48,350
Don't call him Shen Zhiheng.

276
00:23:48,560 --> 00:23:50,110
You should call him Heng.

277
