330
00:25:49,150 --> 00:25:50,960
Mi Lan is pure and naive.

331
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:53,480
You should feed her whatever she likes.

332
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:56,190
Try to make her as happy as possible.

333
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:58,080
