over the arrival of a new year.

345
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:10,320
What does that mean?

346
00:27:12,190 --> 00:27:14,560
Lanterns and fireworks
light up the new year.

347
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:18,110
On Chinese New Year's Eve, lights
are bright and fireworks are everywhere.

348
00:27:18,390 --> 00:27:19,590
Rumor has it

349
00:27:19,870 --> 00:27:23,150
that it'll help us to gain wealth
and prosperity in the coming year.

350
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:25,760
So we shouldn't sleep
on Chinese New Year's Eve.

351
00:27:25,950 --> 00:27:27,790
That's keeping
watch over the arrival of a new year.

352
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:30,350
Aren't Weilian and the rest
going to join us, then?

353
00:27:31,430 --> 00:27:32,800
They're too lazy.

354
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:34,190
I can do it myself.

355
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:36,190
Let's do it together, then.

356
00:27:37,320 --> 00:27:37,960
Okay.

357
00:28:51,190 --> 00:28:53,630
(The hibiscus tree is no longer
in the research center.)

358
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:55,630
(I don't know who took it away.)

359
00:28:56,590 --> 00:28:59,390
(Now, I only have
the Fantasy Stone with me.)

360
00:28:59,910 --> 00:29:01,720
(I have to resolve this
as soon as possible.)

361
00:29:06,700 --> 00:29:09,240
(I've seen the Profound Yang Stone
and set up the hibiscus tree.)

362
00:29:09,760 --> 00:29:12,240
(Its intense power
is the most likely to cause harm.)

363
00:29:12,870 --> 00:29:14,670
(So, who can use
the Profound Yang Stone?)

364
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:16,390
(Future generations should
remember this carefully.)

365
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:19,060
(The descendants of the Mo family
may reactivate the hibiscus tree.)

366
00:29:19,070 --> 00:29:21,490
(They will only be able to utilize the
stone's power with good intention.)

367
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:25,080
(Shen Zhiheng possesses
the power of the Blood Amber Stone.)

368
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:27,680
(If I transfer the power
of the Profound Yang Stone to him,)

369
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:30,000
