(Mi Mansion)

372
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:11,520
You're here, huh?

373
00:30:16,150 --> 00:30:18,040
So, this is what you look like.

374
00:30:18,560 --> 00:30:20,150
Why are your clothes torn?

375
00:30:23,670 --> 00:30:25,720
You kept me company in the past.

376
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:28,040
Sorry about this.

377
00:30:28,320 --> 00:30:29,960
I've left you alone here.

378
00:30:56,910 --> 00:30:58,350
Is there anyone else home?

379
00:31:11,480 --> 00:31:12,150
Who's there?

380
00:31:15,800 --> 00:31:16,560
Mi Lan?

381
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:18,320
What are you doing here?

382
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:20,240
Didn't you run away with Shen Zhiheng?

383
00:31:20,910 --> 00:31:22,560
Didn't you elope with that coachman?

384
00:31:22,830 --> 00:31:23,910
That scoundrel.

385
00:31:23,990 --> 00:31:25,590
He ran away
after cheating me of my money.

386
00:31:46,910 --> 00:31:47,520
You...

387
00:31:48,910 --> 00:31:50,350
You can see now?

388
00:31:52,150 --> 00:31:53,390
How could that be?

389
00:31:53,620 --> 00:31:54,720
I won't tell you the reason.

390
00:31:57,430 --> 00:31:58,590
Shen Zhiheng

391
00:31:59,630 --> 00:32:00,830
is pretty nice to you, huh?

392
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:02,760
He gave you food

393
00:32:03,040 --> 00:32:04,110
and apparel.

394
00:32:04,900 --> 00:32:06,110
He even cured your condition.

395
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:08,910
Where's Shen Zhiheng?

396
00:32:09,980 --> 00:32:11,300
I'm considered his mother-in-law.

397
00:32:11,300 --> 00:32:12,870
He should come here and kowtow to me.

398
00:32:13,350 --> 00:32:14,830
He abducted my daughter.

399
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:16,190
But now, he doesn't dare
to show himself.

400
00:32:16,760 --> 00:32:18,320
He's just a coward...

401
00:32:18,320 --> 00:32:18,910
Shut up!

402
00:32:20,350 --> 00:32:21,630
You dare to talk back to me now?

403
00:32:21,800 --> 00:32:23,290
Seems like you're itching for a beating.

404
00:32:23,800 --> 00:32:24,280
You!

405
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:33,480
Mi Lan!

406
00:32:35,760 --> 00:32:36,280
Stop.

407
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:48,000
Come with me.

408
00:33:01,590 --> 00:33:02,670
You don't need to be afraid.

409
00:33:04,430 --> 00:33:05,800
You did raise Mi Lan after all.

410
00:33:05,910 --> 00:33:07,150
No one wants you dead

411
00:33:07,150 --> 00:33:08,670
because of something like that.

412
00:33:09,560 --> 00:33:11,430
But I do have something
to discuss with you.

413
00:33:11,910 --> 00:33:12,560
Have a seat.

414
00:33:17,590 --> 00:33:19,190
Go ahead. I'm all ears.

415
00:33:25,470 --> 00:33:26,590
Judging from your condition,

416
00:33:27,600 --> 00:33:29,390
I suppose you didn't lead
a comfortable life out there.

417
00:33:29,390 --> 00:33:31,000
That's why you came back, right?

418
00:33:33,870 --> 00:33:34,800
That scoundrel.

419
00:33:35,630 --> 00:33:37,280
He ran away after taking my money!

420
00:33:38,860 --> 00:33:41,140
I can promise you
that you won't need to fret about money

421
00:33:41,150 --> 00:33:42,240
after this.

422
00:33:43,870 --> 00:33:46,480
But you have to be
a good mother for once.

423
00:34:22,790 --> 00:34:23,590
Mi Lan,

424
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:25,920
it was all my fault in the past.

425
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:27,480
Can you please forgive me?

426
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:29,000
I'll apologize to you.

427
00:34:30,630 --> 00:34:33,480
I missed you, you know?

428
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:38,440
Mr. Shen,

429
00:34:39,080 --> 00:34:40,190
let's head home.

430
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:20,360
(Bringing a child into the world
without nurturing or teaching)

431
00:35:20,590 --> 00:35:22,440
(is the worst thing a parent can do.)

432
00:35:23,040 --> 00:35:25,310
(Mi Lan was blind since birth.)

433
00:35:25,670 --> 00:35:27,040
(That was already tragic enough.)

434
00:35:27,420 --> 00:35:29,000
(But you abused her without any reason.)

435
00:35:29,150 --> 00:35:31,480
You even blamed her for your suffering,

436
00:35:31,750 --> 00:35:33,840
