454
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,560
In the past, you loved to lecture me.

455
00:37:03,940 --> 00:37:05,670
You even established
the Six Rules for me.

456
00:37:06,590 --> 00:37:08,080
Although I was obedient,

457
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:10,840
I was upset with it.

458
00:37:11,310 --> 00:37:12,590
But today,

459
00:37:13,630 --> 00:37:15,110
I finally understood why.

460
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:19,230
My parents never taught me anything.

461
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:22,080
Therefore, my knowledge of the world

462
00:37:22,270 --> 00:37:23,710
