avoid detours in life.

464
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:29,480
You don't want me to suffer that much.

465
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:32,360
I can see that.

466
00:37:35,150 --> 00:37:36,630
I'm very happy

467
